Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了 对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.33,0:21:39.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.84,0:21:44.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.21,0:21:50.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.51,0:21:56.27,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.85,0:21:58.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hdc\3a&Hdc\4a&Hdc}Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.89,0:22:09.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.74,0:22:20.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.49,0:22:28.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能   太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.88,0:22:33.81,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.25,0:22:44.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是暗号的解决篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的提示却暗藏巨大的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.40,0:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为帮忙开发新玩具而获得丰厚酬金的阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定带着元太他们去玩寻宝游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是阿笠博士的叔父的别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在叔父去世后的50年之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该不会有人进来的别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却好像有人在这里住过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还发现一些奇妙的图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.84,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现花瓶或是盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有烛台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.43,0:02:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着星星、月亮跟太阳所组合而成的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而博士为了寻宝游戏所藏的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部被某个人给弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得这个别墅好像隐藏着什么巨大的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.26,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在别墅里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次找到7个画有暗号的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法语字典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.21,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.47,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.16,0:02:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肖像画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿笠博士想起了从前阿姨给他看的那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有寄信人地址和名字的信件四周也有同样的暗号图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.81,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那些信还拿给推理小说家 也就是我的爸爸看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小说家发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些暗号全都是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.52,0:03:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来写那些信和画这里的暗号应该是同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.73,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人为什么要写那些暗号给我阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不想让阿姨以外的人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如他正在被某人追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经你这么一说 阿姨曾经说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个怪人经常偷她的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那家伙就是弄坏玩具的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋别墅果然不简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太阳的秘密(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算知道这些暗号是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也还不知道是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不难 只要找出它的规律就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如黑色的太阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的太阳 月亮 星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑色的月亮 星星里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有和它们相似的图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有黑色太阳没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在平假名里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.91,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既无段也无行的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既无段也无行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ん」 是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色太阳原来就是代表ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要注意的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有暗号后面都有三个同样的记号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这三个图案和前面的图案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不同意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是在图形旁的那些小黑点和小白点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右下角那个小黑点虽然还不知道是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过右上角的那些白点和黑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.83,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从位置上来看 很有可能是平假名的浊音和半浊音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是浊音和半浊音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前学校不是教过了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浊音就是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从が行 ざ行右上角的「"」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而半浊音就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぱぴぷぺぽ右上角的「。」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再配合暗号来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些往上翘的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黑点的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有白点的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有什么都没有的月亮 共三种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三种往上翘的月亮可能是は行里的其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有浊音和半浊音的只有は行而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最容易读的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画在这酒杯底的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掉前面三个 从第四个开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个黑色的太阳是ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四个是ぱ行里的其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.04,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个字而且其中有ん和ぱ行的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤 发夹 鹈鹕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆面包 香瓜面包 咖哩面包…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算机 日本 电灯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是写着「扑克牌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果是这样的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这烛台上画的暗号…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个字是ぷ 第四个字是ら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぷ… ら…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋桨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是螺旋桨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果这个黑色的月亮是ろ的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暗号是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぷろぺら…ろ…ろ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.28,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みろ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看螺旋桨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机的暗号就是画在螺旋桨上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果右上方的黑点是「"」的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个字是ぶ 第三个字是ら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぶら…をみろ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.25,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぶら…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油画？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看油画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指这幅肖像画吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些暗号全是别墅里的某一样东西的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面加个「看」字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.51,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说跟着这个提示 就可以找到某样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是只能用暗号才能找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的某个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.97,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我们将所有的暗号解开 然后获得宝藏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的藏有宝藏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道是不是宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里一定隐藏着什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子上画的暗号是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.75,0:07:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个字是ん 第二个字加有浊音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,か び ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字典上面的暗号是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ん…ろ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暖炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡娃娃上面的暗号是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わいんぐらす…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止知道的文字有17个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它空白部分用其它图案来做推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在写什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是暗号的解读表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看可以就发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳 月亮 星星分别代表「あいうえお」各段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.48,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后它们是根据同一规则横向变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如太阳和星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们周围尖尖的部分都是按顺时针方向逐一减少一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而月亮也是按顺时针方向缺角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于图形右下角的黑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是图形不够用才加上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.68,0:09:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后利用这个解读表把所有的暗号解读出来 就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看烛台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看螺旋桨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看油画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看傀儡娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看法语词典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看暖炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说宝藏在暖炉里面啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 什么都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗号 刻在地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 把刚才的解读表拿给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个暗号是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别卖关子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子… 是指最初的那个盘子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这样不就又回到起点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被这些暗号给耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这讨厌的恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧？ 怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人利用这种可能解不开的暗号恶作剧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果照着暗号来看就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个解读表有什么地方弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些暗号的顺序之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么真正的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 在警方来这里之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先把东西放回原来的位置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子是在碗柜里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果把盘子 花瓶前面的那些字连起来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さがろぷあれにわとふだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是用罗马拼音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烛台是放在暖炉的上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架飞机是放在哪里的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.92,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本来放在花瓶旁边 是我拿到寝室里面去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶的旁边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它想成英文呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 法语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是德文呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个想得明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该来帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要坐在房间中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得扑克牌好像也是在这房间里面的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本放在时钟的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿来用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画有暗号的东西全部都在这房间里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.27,0:12:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果将它们依照顺序串联起来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烛台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋桨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法语字典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线刚好集中在房间中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪步美一直在我旁边走来走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了 房间中央就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一点可疑的地方也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在地板的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板的吊灯有条沟槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 快过来背我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.13,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼好像有什么东西掉下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.06,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那间房间的正上方应该是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间里面竟然有楼梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个暗号是暗示天花板的吊灯有机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是指这个隐藏的楼梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说叔父喜欢玩这种机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然真的有这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道宝藏就在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面一定隐藏着什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先把窗户打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻中的一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是画油画的颜料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 桌子上好像有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宝藏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 说清楚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个人是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里住着一位手指灵活的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻一元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟画暗号的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是他这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他是被杀的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.38,0:16:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.12,0:16:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在写信给你阿姨的时候去世的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他的心脏好像不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.15,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他为什么会在这个房间里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.95,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这里的应该只有住在这里的叔父和阿姨才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有一个人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.70,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你叔父去世之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经在这里出现过的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父去世之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个画家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暖炉旁边的你阿姨和叔父的画像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是画那幅画的画家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他大概是在画画时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叔父提起过这个房间的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他为什么要藏在这里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要用暗号信寄给阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想原因大概就是这个吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.02,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20元美钞的模板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假钞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.37,0:17:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是受人委托的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是后来他大概良心不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便和模板一起消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.04,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了躲那个人才偷偷住在这里吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信给你阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想感谢她让他住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以用暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.63,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不想让其它人知道他躲在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么阿姨说的那个偷信的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是制造假钞的委托人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.47,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也是将博士藏起来的那些玩具给割坏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为可以找到那个模板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道里面竟然是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我把它们给割烂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听说他和这里的主人很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直怀疑他还躲在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还有这个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们这些小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.93,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.36,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果打中模板的话 那就没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.40,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从老头子手中拿模板过来给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.51,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我之后 叔叔会奖赏你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭…臭小子 存心找死吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急什么急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.43,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西待会再给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥田伦明…先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体怎么可能会说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.48,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细听的话就听得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的亡灵一定还在这里徘徊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭小子 挺大胆的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥田伦明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥田伦明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥田伦明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥田伦明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.29,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信守承诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把东西给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我们趁现在快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小心亡灵又跑回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个　这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人变声器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我趁机录下自己的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以慢速度重复播放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.35,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是怎么知道他的名字的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桌上那封写了一半的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的暗号写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.36,0:20:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不想把这件艺术品交给奥田伦明」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.91,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定想把这件艺术品交给阿姨保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.29,0:20:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才留下表明自己藏身在这别墅里的暗号啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你阿姨现在人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年去世了 享年76岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还一直单身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.59,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是为了答谢她而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两小时后 警方赶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕了奥田伦明那个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于可以回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.75,0:23:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸说的那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就像太阳一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.36,0:23:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后有一段时间 他都叫我太阳博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是指这件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.20,0:23:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是比喻而已啊 比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.09,0:23:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.47,0:23:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个解读表解读博士的名字看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.26,0:23:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是太阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.98,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是太阳博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.85,0:23:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…外面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我们两个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连我们也骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.15,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.49,0:24:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.69,0:24:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团消失事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.85,0:24:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.02,0:24:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶的数量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次侦探团大活跃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是我
